title: #92Noon! Friday Football Feast! Greenway/Cray
description: PA and Charch are back to preview the first game of the Vikings preseason! Chad Greenway joins to talk Grey Duck, Vikes, and his career. Then 5-Time Grammy winner Robert Cray joins to talk music and his upcoming show.
